# Playwright Test Suite

This repository contains automated **UI and API tests** using Playwright.  
It covers testing of [FakeStore API](https://fakestoreapi.com/) and [Restful-Booker API](https://restful-booker.herokuapp.com/), as well as any UI interactions you may add.

---

## Project Structure

tests/
├─ api/ # API test files
└─ ui/ # UI test files


- `api/` - contains tests for GET, POST, PUT, DELETE requests.
- `ui/` - contains tests for user interface interactions, if applicable.

---

## Setup

1. **Clone the repository**

```bash
git clone <your-repo-url>
cd <repo-folder>

Install dependencies

npm install

Install Playwright browsers

npx playwright install


Running Tests

Run all tests

npx playwright test

Run only API tests

npx playwright test tests/api

Run only UI tests

npx playwright test tests/ui

Run a specific test file

npx playwright test tests/api/booking.spec.js


Run in headed mode (see browser interactions)

npx playwright test --headed

Run with debug logs

npx playwright test --debug


